summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Aircabio airport transfer booking website. Backend APIs are 100% functional, but critical frontend integration issues prevent complete booking flow and admin access.

ui_bugs.issue: Calendar opens but date selection fails - clicking dates doesn't register selection
ui_bugs.impact: Blocks entire booking flow - users cannot complete bookings

ui_bugs.issue: Admin login form doesn't authenticate despite backend API working

integration_issues.issue: Cannot navigate to search results due to date picker validation failure
Frontend login form not properly integrating with backend auth API

passed_tests: Homepage loads with booking engine visible
Navigation links work (Our Fleet, About Us, FAQ, Contact)
Booking form fields can be filled (pickup, dropoff, time, passengers, luggage, flight number)
All backend APIs (11/11) - vehicles, pricing, quotes, auth, bookings, admin stats
action_item_for_main_agent: Fix critical frontend issues: 1) Date picker component not registering date selections in BookingEngine, 2) Admin login form not properly authenticating with backend API. Both issues prevent core functionality from working.
